"{\"uid\": \"gnlm.com.mm-thet-htar-thuzar-quits-paris-olympics-after-narrow-loss\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Myanmar badminton star Thet Htar Thuzar has left the 2024 Olympic Badminton Tournament after suffering a shock loss to a Canadian player by only two points.The 25-year-old Thet Htar Thuzar, ranking 43rd in the world, was able to play with the same ability against 32-year-old Canadian player Michelle Li, ranking 32nd in the world.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myanmar\", \"score\": 0.9999999978358574, \"rank\": 2.134981664720094e-09, \"text\": \"Myanmar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myanmar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myanmar\"}, {\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thet Htar Thuzar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9861855812257179, \"rank\": 0.012456416407949181, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thet Htar Thuzar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thet_Htar_Thuzar\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9861855812257179, \"rank\": 0.012456416407949181, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso